4) Ethics, Risks, and Constraints Traceability 

Legal/ethical/privacy constraints: 

• Privacy by default (no cloud upload) -> TW-REQ-008. 

• Platform/licensing: document frameworks/models used (to be added after consolidation). 

Top risks (with mitigation/acceptance): 

• Model accuracy variance -> collect diverse test clips; freeze thresholds pre-test; calibrate camera placement. 

• Latency/thermal trade-offs -> maintain ≥15 fps; use lightweight smoothing; monitor thermal state. 

• Over-reliance on cues -> disclaimers; position as guidance, not medical advice. 

 

